  "disclaimer": {
    "title": "Disclaimer",
    "back": "Back to Home",
    "intro": "The data displayed on the 'Cene sa pijace' portal is collected automatically and is intended solely for informational purposes. By using this website, the user accepts the terms and conditions outlined below.",
    "sourceHeading": "Data Source",
    "sourceBody": "All agricultural product price data on our portal is sourced from official and publicly available channels. The primary data sources are the official STIPS system (Agricultural Market Information System of Serbia), managed by the Ministry of Agriculture, Forestry and Water Management, as well as official websites of public utility companies (JKP) that manage local green markets across Serbia. The 'Cene sa pijace' portal is an independent digital solution solely intended to process, structure, and visually present this public data to make daily market tracking easier for citizens. This portal is not an official state or municipal authority, nor is it associated in any way with the aforementioned Ministry or utility companies.",
    "liabilityHeading": "Limitation of Liability",
    "liabilityBody1": "While we make reasonable efforts to ensure the displayed data remains up to date, we do not guarantee its absolute accuracy, completeness, or timeliness. Green market prices change in real time and may deviate from the last recorded values due to seasonal, market, or logistical factors beyond our control.",
    "liabilityBody2": "The 'Cene sa pijace' portal is not liable for any inaccuracies or errors resulting from manual data entry by authorized market personnel, nor for any technical failures during data transmission from the source systems.",
    "liabilityBody3": "The data displayed on this website is not considered official and should not be used as the sole basis for legal, financial, or commercial decisions. For official and up-to-date information, please refer directly to the STIPS system or the competent Ministry."
  },
